# CSG Component Builder

Generate production-ready React components matching the CSG Design System defined in `DESIGN.md`.

## Output per component
1. `.tsx` — React component with TypeScript props
2. `.module.css` — CSS Module using design token custom properties
3. Brief usage example

## Code standards

```tsx
import styles from './ComponentName.module.css'

interface ComponentNameProps {
  // explicit prop types
}

export function ComponentName({ ...props }: ComponentNameProps) {
  return (...)
}
```

## Key specs from DESIGN.md

### Colors (always use CSS custom properties)
```css
--primary-500: #8FC31F;    /* Primary CTA */
--primary-400: #A8E03C;    /* Hover */
--primary-600: #76A219;    /* Pressed */
--secondary-500: #003A4A;  /* Dark text, teal accents */
--neutral-50: #FAFAFA;     /* Recessed chrome */
--neutral-700: #404040;    /* Body text */
--neutral-900: #171717;    /* Heading text */
--error: #DC2626;
--border: #E5E5E5;
--border-regular: #D9D9D9;
```

### Typography
- EN: `'Space Grotesk', ui-sans-serif, system-ui`
- CN: `'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif`
- Code/IDs: `'Space Mono', ui-monospace, monospace`

### Icons — MingCute only
```tsx
import { Icon } from '@iconify/react'
<Icon icon="mingcute:close-line" width={18} height={18} />
```
Always use `-line` variants unless `-fill` is semantically required.

### Component dimensions
- Text button: Small=28px, Default=36px, Large=42px
- Text input: 42px height, #FAFAFA bg, 8px radius
- Card: #FFFFFF bg, 1px solid #E5E5E5, 12px radius, 24px padding
- Badge: 9999px radius, 4px 10px padding, 12px font
- Pop-up: 422px wide, 12px radius, shadow 0px 10px 24px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)

### Disabled state (all components)
- `opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed;`

## Rules
1. Read `DESIGN.md` for exact specs before generating
2. Use `var(--token)` — never hardcode hex values
3. Use `@iconify/react` with `mingcute:` prefix only
4. Implement all states: default, hover, pressed, disabled, error
5. Match Figma pixel values exactly
6. Use named exports, not default
